node.text:
Featuring the 𝐍𝐞𝐰 𝐅𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐲 𝐒𝐞𝐭 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐥 $𝟔𝟗.𝟗𝟎 (𝚞𝚜𝚞𝚊𝚕 𝚙𝚛𝚒𝚌𝚎 𝚊𝚝 𝚂$𝟾𝟿.𝟿𝟶) from my fave Thai food restaurant @WangThaiKitchen that comes with 6 delectable dishes as below:⁣
⁣
⭐️Thai Style Grilled Chicken ⁣
⭐️Tom Yam Seafood Soup⁣
⭐️Thai Style Grilled Pork⁣
⭐️Pineapple Fried Rice⁣
⭐️Thai Fried Kway Chap with Cai Po⁣
⭐️Mango Salad with Fish Skin⁣
⁣
Add on Thai lced milk tea with pearls $2 (Usual Price $3.50)⁣
⁣
Islandwide delivery! Call 63582938/93847588 for more information! ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Thank you Nelly @PopstarMedia and @WangThaiKitchen for the delivering the delicious meal. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣

Blk 92 Toa Payoh Lorong 4⁣⁣⁣⁣
Unit No.: 01-274⁣⁣⁣⁣
Singapore 310092⁣⁣⁣⁣
